- Import from @atproto/oauth-client-browser
- Hardcode metadata fields that the NodeOAuthClient already provides (client_id, redirect_uris, etc.)
- Use "use client"
- Remove the NextRequest parameter if needed for the function signature (actually, the GET handler doesnt need it — just use `GET()`)

